# This repo ships code only — no game data, no derived data, no art. Golden
# characterization fixtures (tree data.json, atlas frame-maps, art hashes) and
# any GGPK extract live OUTSIDE the repo, located via env vars at test time
# (POE2_TREE_GOLDEN / POE2_TREE_DATA / POE2_GGPK_EXTRACT). Defensive ignores in
# case anything is ever regenerated into the tree:
**/test/golden/
**/*.dds
**/*.csd
**/*.psg

